description:
Teen Coin a cryptocurrency geared towards youth  integrated  into a network around the globe, from schools, to community groups, and larger scale investors.

It provides education about blockchain technologies. Having fun with teen coin playing games and building social networks.

It can remove the problem of having to deal with a specific merchant, and can be used for local trading, buying, selling, and as a open-source business tool.
name: MyTeenCoin
